{
  "stem": "17299.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train was pulling out, and we were just in the open country when two American fighter bombers attacked the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The two engines got shot out, and a number of SS and some prisoners got killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the German guards jumped right off the train and surrounded the whole train so that nobody should escape.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were sitting there for-- the Americans dropped some bombs on the town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The town was called [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Reitzenheim. ?] And we tried to get away from this,and the population came right away and were very hostile.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sudeten Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and the SS.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some Sudeten Germans came right away out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were-- had to pick up a few SS men to take him to a-- a hospital, who got wounded.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he came back, the Germans were separating the healthy ones from the sick ones already.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to line up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then a car with six men came on with machine pistols.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they start to open fire right away at the-- at the sick ones.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they picked out maybe a dozen fellows and told them, you stay here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You throw the bodies in the box car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I was marched off towards Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were marched in groups of 200.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were maybe 25 SS men in the-- guarding the 200. 10 on each side and five in the back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after a while, we heard some shooting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyone who fell behind or could not keep up got shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Into Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were told that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the first night, we were in a factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a house nearby, and some fellows stole a few potatoes because we had nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
